
xgrid(2)                       Scilab Function                       xgrid(2)
NAME
  xgrid - add a grid on a graphic

CALLING SEQUENCE
  xgrid([style])

PARAMETERS

  style     : an integer

DESCRIPTION
  Adds a grid on a 2D plot. style stands for the dash style or color to use
  for the grid plotting.

EXAMPLE
  plot2d()
  xgrid()

SEE ALSO
  xset, plot2d

